      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国调查人员寻求延长对尹某的逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/south-korean-corruption-watchdog-asks-police-to-arrest-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国反腐监督机构申请延长逮捕总统尹锡烈的逮捕令，此前上周，他们与总统安保团队进行了长达数小时的对峙，最终以失败告终。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/south-korean-corruption-watchdog-asks-police-to-arrest-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 00:20:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克转而攻击法拉奇，斯塔默难得得到喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/musk-extends-intervention-in-uk-politics-with-attack-on-farage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 亲身体验了即将到来的特朗普时代的混乱政治，他的政府整个周末都在抵御埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的攻击，结果却看到这位亿万富翁煽动者背叛了他昔日的英国盟友奈杰尔·法拉奇 (Nigel Farage)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/musk-extends-intervention-in-uk-politics-with-attack-on-farage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示英国商业信心跌至特拉斯迷你预算以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/business-morale-sinks-to-lowest-since-truss-mini-budget-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国商会的一项调查显示，英国商业信心已跌至两年多前前保守党首相利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 灾难性的小型预算以来的最低水平，这一调查反映了人们对现任工党政府增税的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/business-morale-sinks-to-lowest-since-truss-mini-budget-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对党领袖在选举僵局中加大赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/mozambique-opposition-leader-plans-to-return-home-on-jan-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对派领导人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 自去年 10 月有争议的选举以来指挥了一波又一波的抗议活动，导致数十人丧生。他计划本周晚些时候结束自我流放回国，这可能会加剧这个东南部非洲国家的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/mozambique-opposition-leader-plans-to-return-home-on-jan-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 18:53:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
